      'การนำโค้ดเดิมเข้าสู่ระบบใช้เหตุผลกับโค้ดเบสจริงและปรับให้สอดคล้องแทนการเขียนทับ จากนั้นตรวจสอบความสอดคล้อง',
  },
} as const;
const t = i18n[lang as keyof typeof i18n] ?? i18n.en;
---

<figure class={`editorial-asset onboard ${className}`} role="img" aria-label={t.ariaLabel}>
  <div class="editorial-asset__grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="editorial-asset__body">
    <ol class="onboard-row">
      {
        t.steps.map((s, i) => (
          <li class="onboard-step">
            <span class={`onboard-chip${i === t.steps.length - 1 ? ' onboard-chip--accent' : ''}`}>
              <span class="onboard-num nums-tabular">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
              {s}
            </span>
            {i < t.steps.length - 1 && (
              <span class="onboard-arrow" aria-hidden="true">
                →
              </span>
            )}
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ol>
    <p class="onboard-note">{t.note}</p>
  </div>
  <figcaption class="fig-caption">{t.caption}</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .onboard {
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .onboard-row {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .onboard-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex: 1 1 auto;
  }
  .onboard-chip {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.65rem 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    background-color: var(--color-paper);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .onboard-chip--accent {
    border-color: var(--color-secondary);
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }
  .onboard-num {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .onboard-chip--accent .onboard-num {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }
  .onboard-arrow {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }
  .onboard-note {
    margin: 0.85rem 0 0;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
